{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaList","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaList","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaList\"><code>MediaList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaList/mediaText\"><code>mediaText</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>MediaList</strong></code>&nbsp;接口表示样式表的媒体查询，例如使用了&nbsp;<code>media</code>&nbsp;属性的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a> 元素。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>注意：</strong><code>MediaList</code>&nbsp;是一个实时列表；使用以下属性或方法更新列表会立刻更新文档的表现。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"medialist.mediatext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaList/mediaText\"><code>MediaList.mediaText</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>一个字符串转化器，返回一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，以文本形式表示&nbsp;<code>MediaList</code>，也可以通过这个方法设置新的&nbsp;<code>MediaList</code>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"medialist.length\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaList.length</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回&nbsp;<code>MediaList</code>&nbsp;中媒体查询的数量。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"medialist.appendmedium\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaList.appendMedium()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>向&nbsp;<code>MediaList</code>&nbsp;中添加一个媒体查询。</dd>\n <dt id=\"medialist.deletemedium\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaList.deleteMedium()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>从&nbsp;<code>MediaList</code>&nbsp;中移除一个媒体查询。</dd>\n <dt id=\"medialist.item\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>MediaList.item()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>一个获取函数，返回一个<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>CSSOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>，表示文本形式的媒体查询，需要提供媒体查询在&nbsp;<code>MediaList</code>&nbsp;中的索引位置。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下述例子会在控制台记录 <code>MediaList</code>&nbsp;的文本表示，其来自应用到当前文档的第一个样式表。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> stylesheets <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> stylesheet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stylesheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>media<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mediaText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-medialist-interface","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"}],"query":"api.MediaList"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaList","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaList/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"MediaList 接口表示样式表的媒体查询，例如使用了 media 属性的<link> 元素。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaList","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaList","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/medialist","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/medialist/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaList","title":"MediaList"}],"pageTitle":"MediaList - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}